<p>2、https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lxneek9fGbQ </p>
<p>3、https://ai.facebook.com/blog/state-of-the-art-open-source-chatbot </p>
<p>4、https://home.pandorabots.com/bot_battle.html </p>
<p>5、https://www.technologyreview.com/2020/04/29/1000795/facebook-ai-chatbot-blender-beats-google-meena/ </p>
